import pyautogui
import time
import uiautomation as auto

try:
    # Press Win key to open Start menu
    pyautogui.hotkey('win')
    time.sleep(1)
    # Type "notepad" to search
    pyautogui.typewrite('notepad')
    time.sleep(1)
    # Press Enter to launch
    pyautogui.press('enter')
    time.sleep(2)
    # Verify Notepad window exists
    np = auto.WindowControl(searchDepth=1, ClassName='Notepad')
    if np.Exists(3, 1):
        print("EXECUTION_SUCCESS")
    else:
        print("FAILED: Notepad window not found")
except Exception as e:
    print(f"FAILED: {e}")
